OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1778217995
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 22 May to Fri 5 JunFLow
OL,6,Fpressure systems are likely to still
OL,7,Fbe close by to north or northeast of
OL,8,Fthe UK at the start of this period,
OL,9,Fwith a continuation of changeable and
OL,10,Fat times windy conditions most likely
OL,11,Fhere. There will however, probably be
OL,12,Fsome dry and warm interludes, these
OL,13,Fmore likely towards the south
OL,14,Finitially, but these may become rather
OL,15,Fmore widespread through the latter
OL,16,Fpart of this period. Temperatures
OL,17,Fthrough the latter part of May and
OL,18,Finto early June may end up being above
OL,19,Faverage overall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
